        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/82dd89/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2025-02-09T02:05:53.383Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Signal needs to brush up its UI. I have been trying to move some people from WhatsApp to Signal and I am failing due to Signal’s UI.</p>\n<p>Namely: Everything looks too big. Too much padding and margins.</p>\n<p>On WhatsApp, I see 8.5 chats. And this is with the big bottom bar that WhatsApp has!</p>\n<p>On Signal, I see 7 chats. And this is with the small/compact bar. Which just shows how much padding/margins Signal has. Way too much.</p>\n<p>It would be nice if Signal provided a more compact/dense view.</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 5,
        "updated_at": "2025-02-09T02:05:53.383Z",
